¶ For a three hour tour ¶

00:21.288 --> 00:24.055
¶ A three hour tour ¶

00:24.124 --> 00:25.557
[thunder rumbling]

00:25.626 --> 00:28.226
¶ The weather started
     getting rough ¶

00:28.295 --> 00:30.629
¶ The tiny ship was tossed ¶

00:30.697 --> 00:33.098
¶ If not for the courage
    of the fearless crew ¶

00:33.167 --> 00:35.200
¶ The Minnow would be lost ¶

00:35.269 --> 00:37.469
¶ The Minnow would be lost ¶

