¶ The ship set ground
     on the shore ¶

00:39.573 --> 00:42.407
¶ Of this uncharted
      desert isle ¶

00:42.476 --> 00:44.976
¶ With Gilligan ¶

00:45.045 --> 00:47.111
¶ The Skipper too ¶

00:47.180 --> 00:49.214
¶ The millionaire ¶

00:49.283 --> 00:51.783
¶ And his wife ¶

00:51.852 --> 00:54.619
¶ The movie star ¶

